\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但人數分散晒好易比人清埸, 人少的話和理非驚比人拉會唔敢出黎行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"89e4cba9c719fb1a2f649ec31cd9644a11ee7e01","tid":1379781,"uid":41700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9e2fbe63638cc016851333316195b9955072564","tid":1379781,"uid":262557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:52:56.000Z","msg":"老實講十八區太多<br />\n會唔夠人<br />\n逐步試<br />\n可以3-5區先<br />\n人多就谷<br />\n人少就縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:19:00.000Z","msg":"其實可以試行幾區先，最ideal就梗係18區一齊嚟啦<br />\n我相信成本低咗，出嚟行嘅人會多咗"},{"pid":"d6595b224a35f10843e6553dc0d846c8f4f749af","tid":1379781,"uid":41700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:50:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"59d80cb3b00df55061a21658bd16ff7a7eacc743","tid":1379781,"uid":88610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:55:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79c6a1b370d906f1a0ee832e27b8c14a06f401a0","tid":1379781,"uid":41700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:34:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42d86b6e3467f8eaa0742b7cc04890c4fe2f1ca4","tid":1379781,"uid":267196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e22e2cf5c9154a046f5ad4c0825c43b0d58f46e","tid":1379781,"uid":18470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:46:02.000Z","msg":"實唔會批 和理非準備好一齊非法集結未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:50: